        "Verification",
        "First Login",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三个section。在注册表单阶段，除了正常的填写和提交，是否需要体现错误场景？比如密码强度不够或者用户名已被占用的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error weak password",
        "Error duplicate username/email",
        "Submit registration form"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个错误场景都要放进去。密码太弱和重复注册信息是用户最常遇到的卡点，评分可以低一些，2分比较合适。正常操作比如打开页面、填写信息都是5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error weak password",
        "Error duplicate username/email",
        "Open registration page",
        "Enter username, email, password"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，注册部分我先这样画。接下来验证环节，系统发送验证邮件后，用户点击链接，这里也要考虑token过期或无效的情况对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "System sends verification email",
        "User clicks verification link",
        "Error expired or invalid token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，验证失败要给2分。验证成功后进入最后阶段：用户用刚注册的账号登录，系统创建认证会话，可以选做2FA设置，最后重定向到Dashboard。这个跳转体验要顺畅，给5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Successful verification",
        "User logs in with credentials",
        "System creates auth session",
        "optional 2FA setup",
        "Redirect to Dashboard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，系统创建会话和可选的2FA这部分，评分3分是因为涉及后台处理对吧？另外整个图表的标题用\"User Journey: Registration & Account Activation\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "System creates auth session + optional 2FA setup",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标题没问题。3分是因为创建会话有延迟，而且2FA设置是可选步骤，会打断流程。不过等等，提交注册表单的评分我刚才说错了——用户提交后等待响应是有焦虑感的，4分更合适，不是5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Submit registration form"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，已将\"Submit registration form\"从5分调整为4分。现在三个阶段都完整了：注册表单包含两个错误分支，验证环节包含token失效处理，首次登录后引导至Dashboard。还有其他需要调整的吗？",
